resolution.summary:
I believe this comes from the stores not re-ordering the series after adding the external labels. You can replicate it by adding the metrics:
```
metric{}
metric{alocal="label"}
```

And an external label `ext="label"`. Before the external label, `metric{} < metric{alocal="label"}` because it has fewer labels.

